::Lynxiz::

	Having finished looking around the control room of the 
Starjumper, she turns to the bot who's name she thought she 
heard was called Wizard. "Hello, Wizard, I'm Lynxiz, I'm kind of 
new here." She extends her hand, "What are we supposed to be 
doing in the control room?" She smiles.
